description: When it comes to his weekly date with Leeroy Jones, Aspen never really knows what kind of situation he'll be walking into. Leeroy likes to keep things weird, and today is no exception, as Aspen enters Leeroy's chambers to discover someone else standing in the corner. Intrigued, Aspen steals a look, but Daddy Leeroy is having none of that disobedience, and immediately punishes Aspen for breaking the rules. Leeroy is stern, with a firm hand and a keen sense of discipline, but he's also very giving (and has plenty to give). Aspen may not ever know what to expect, but he always leaves wanting more, which is just how Leeroy wants it.Enjoy!
title: Dominant Date
